---
import BlogPost from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<BlogPost title="About Me" description="About me" pubDate={new Date('2024-02-24')}>
	<div class="about-container">
		<div class="about-text">
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<p>
				I'm a full-stack engineer and indie developer based in San Diego, specializing in creating applications with a distinct kawaii and cute aesthetic. I believe that software should be both functional and delightful.
			</p>
			<p>
				This philosophy inspired me to create Weavey, an app designed to streamline and de-stress the job application process. My goal is to build tools that are not only powerful but also bring a little joy to the user's day.
			</p>
			<p>
				My professional background includes significant contributions to large-scale projects at major technology companies, where I've had the opportunity to help ship products used by millions.
			</p>
			<p>
				When I'm not at my keyboard, you can usually find me enjoying the San Diego beaches or spending quality time with my cat.
			</p>
		</div>
		<img src="/images/cute selfie.JPG" alt="Marissa's selfie" class="about-selfie" />
	</div>
</BlogPost>

<style>
	.about-container {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 2em;
	}
	.about-text {
		flex: 2;
	}
	.about-selfie {
		flex: 1;
		max-width: 250px;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}
</style>
